Higher Level Help Details at https://www.sqlite.org/draft/cli.html
For Windows Install Sqllite tools or https://sqlitebrowser.org/dl/ for gui feel
Once installed found in the following folder C:\Program Files (x86)\SQLite3Tools
at command prompt enter sqlite3.exe
open you database, for example > .open "file path with forward slashes"
Basic Commands
Show the schema
.schema

List Tables
.tables

Select Query

